## The 26 Columns — A to Z

### Task Identity
| Column | Name | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| A | Checkbox | Task completion checkbox — one click to mark done |
| B | Task ID | Auto-generated unique identifier, categorised by type |
| C | Task Name | Description of the task |
| D | Category | Study, Networking, Admin, Personal, Project, Work, Housework |
| E | Priority | High, Medium, Low |
| F | Status | Not Started, In Progress, Completed |

### Dates & Time Tracking
| Column | Name | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| G | Start Date | Auto-populated when status changes to In Progress |
| H | Due Date | Manual input — deadline for the task |
| I | Completion Date | Auto-populated when status changes to Completed |
| J | Duration in Hours | Calculated from start to completion date |
| K | Duration in Minutes | Calculated from start to completion date |

### Performance & Alerts
| Column | Name | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| L | Days Overdue / Status Alert | Overdue status with colour coding |
| M | Priority Flag | Escalates high priority tasks that are overdue or due soon |
| N | Completion Rate | Running percentage of completed tasks |
| O | Workload by Category | Task count and percentage per category |

### Time Analysis
| Column | Name | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| P | Weekly Task Count | Tasks started in the current week |
| Q | Monthly Task Count | Tasks completed in the current month |
| R | Estimated vs Actual Time | Compares estimated hours to actual duration |
| S | Task Efficiency Score | Rates task completion quality on a 0–100 scale |
| Y | Estimated Time in Hours | Manual input for estimated task duration |
| Z | Estimated Time in Minutes | Auto-converted from Column Y |

### Advanced KPIs
| Column | Name | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| T | Overdue Count by Category | Overdue tasks broken down per category |
| U | Average Completion Time by Category | Average hours to complete tasks per category |
| V | Task Velocity | Tasks completed per week |
| W | Deadline Adherence Rate | Percentage of on-time completions |
| X | Overall Productivity Score | Composite productivity score out of 100 |

